game.name: Coloring Cars Time
game.description:
Everyone wants to own his dream car. What better it would be if you get a chance to color your dream car? Would you like to color multiple car models with a combination of your favorite colors? Join Coloring Cars Time and be prepared to choose one of the three cars and color it you like! Hey friends! There are no color limits and you would have a full freedom to play with your imaginations. Give it a try at least once to know how this brand new arcade challenge can help to keep you entertained for hours!

Start this fun challenge by selecting your car models and get ready to color its different body parts including the front side, light, wheel, body, window and hubcap of your vehicle! Put your coloring abilities to the test to create your colorful cars in this html5 coloring game! You can start coloring from any body part as per your choice. For example, the window looks awesome in black or white color. You can color its body with red, front side with blue, light with yellow, a wheel with black and hubcap with any other color you want.

Experiment your color imaginations on all the three car models and show off the world that how innovative you are in this cool kids coloring game! You can try out other free color games to improve and practice your coloring skills in a friendly environment. Our all arcade challenges are free to play online and it is up to you what game you choose and allow yourself to have fun without download.
